Manheiher, Respondent, v. Schneittacher, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and Coumty, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from fifth district court.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Van Hoesen, J.

Boardman & Boardman, for appellant. A. H. Berrick, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
